在哪？"}, "image_area": {"url": ""}, "metrics_area": {"text": "732 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/522430505"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8InNGj1MXA8ap6EAMaCDc4Mzc3NTExIMXQypEGMCU4jApACHIJNTIyNDMwNTA1eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "9_1647781842.2752318", "card_id": "Q_522905172", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 114}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "如何看待俄航天局长称「美国正研究将俄罗斯排除出 GPS 卫星导航系统，俄有格洛纳斯系统无需紧张」？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "当地时间 19 日，俄罗斯航天局局长罗戈津表示，美国正在研究将俄罗斯排除出 GPS 卫星导航系统的问题。 罗戈津说，无需为这一问题感到紧张，因为俄罗斯有格洛纳斯（GLONASS）系统，所有的智能手机都装载了这一系统，即使被切断 GPS 系统也能正常工作。透露，关于乌克兰局势，将敦促莫迪与日美欧等统一步调。不过，由于印度与俄罗斯向来关系友好，能在多大程度上促使印度采取协调路线尚不清楚。俄航天局局长：美国正研究将俄罗斯排除出 GPS 卫星导航系统 _ 欧洲航天局终止与俄罗斯合作 _ 罗戈津 _ 格洛纳斯"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-12143093946afc02c13ac75bbb8d2db8_720w.jpg?source=1940ef5c"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "536 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/522905172"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8InNGj1MXA8ap6EAMaCDc4NDgyNjc2IM2V15EGMAk4lgRACXIJNTIyOTA1MTcyeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "10_1647781842.275928", "card_id": "Q_522469201", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 582}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "俄罗斯到底是想快打乌克兰还是慢打乌克兰？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": " "}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/80/v2-a73828334ee6bf862ff3976668adf100_720w.jpg?source=1940ef5c"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "508 万热度"}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/522469201"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8InNGj1MXA8ap6EAMaCDc4Mzg2MDgzIM69y5EGMCM4+AdACnIJNTIyNDY5MjAxeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "11_1647781842.2765267", "